PODAK CO LTD June Sales Fall 6.70% (Table) : 3537 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-07-08T10:28:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/podak-co-ltd-june-sales-fall-6-70-table-3537-tt.html
PODAK CO LTD (3537)  said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 6.70% to NT$224,302,000 from NT$240,407,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            224,302          240,407    
YOY%              -6.70%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,245,917        1,472,518   
YOY%             -15.39% 
=================================================================
 